<section id="difference" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">The difference</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">AI search converts 5× better than Google.<br/>Are you visible?</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">AI assistants generate 45 billion sessions monthly. ChatGPT alone drives 19.5% of global search traffic. Your site is either in the answer — or it's not.</p>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-14">
			<div class="card p-8 border-red/20">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-muted flex items-center justify-center text-red text-xs font-bold">✗</span>
					<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Without AEOrank</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5 text-sm text-text-muted">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Invisible to ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, Gemini, Google AI Overviews</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>No llms.txt, no ai.txt — AI crawlers have nothing to read</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>GPTBot and ClaudeBot blocked in robots.txt by default</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Content structured for Google, not for AI extraction</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Competitors cited in AI answers — you're not mentioned</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>No way to measure AI visibility or track regressions</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-8 border-accent/20">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-muted flex items-center justify-center text-green text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
					<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">With AEOrank</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5 text-sm text-text">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Score 0–100 across 36 criteria tells you exactly where you stand</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>9 AI-readable files generated — llms.txt, ai.txt, schema.json, more</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>AI crawler access configured correctly for every engine</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Content analyzed for AI extractability across 5 pillars</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Check Runs on every PR — catch AI visibility regressions in CI</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Actionable recommendations — not just scores, but exactly what to fix</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
